{"tid":917033,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"BigBoysToys 將推 Q 版草薙京《拳皇》場景玩具","createTime":"2018-11-26T06:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T06:09:40.000Z","uid":51464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7295971417ed970c12054c80e979f47ff7d2c1d","tid":917033,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2215860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2215860&d=CJoisIZfw18%2B85AXPQ5RqwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cd16bf77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2215860</a><br />\n香港 BigBoysToys 公司之前所推出的 T.N.C. 系列《街霸（Street Fighter）》Q 版場景擺設玩具，將卡通版的阿隆、春麗、軍佬等《街霸》街機遊戲角色，呈現在相應的遊戲地台場景中，再配上華麗的 LED 燈效，設計備受不少玩具迷和遊戲迷好評。最近 BigBoysToys 在旗下 Facebook 專頁中，公開了 T.N.C. 系列草薙京 Q 版場境玩具。相信 BigBoysToys 將會為更多《拳皇（King of Fighters、KOF）》知名街機角色，推出相關的 T.N.C 系列 Q 版場景擺設玩具！<br />\n====<br />\n好似好正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}